overview: On October 22nd Josh Barnett returns to the ring on Bloodsports 7! Already announced is the first match where Marina Shafir takes on Masha Slamovich. Also announced to take part in the event are the two killers from the NJPW LA Dojo - Clark Connors & Alex Coughlin, as well as Minoru Suzuki, Davey Richards, Filthy Tom, Yutu Uemera, Calvin Tankman, Yoya and more!
title: GCW Josh Barnett's Bloodsport 7
